WEBVTT

01:01.064 --> 01:03.627
An Indian Guru who came to Istanbul to teach Yoga is

01:03.652 --> 01:06.300
in the focus of attention of the high society.

01:06.334 --> 01:10.883
See who kneeled before the Indian Guru wanting
to find solutions for their problems.

01:10.923 --> 01:12.923
Gamze Reisoğlu prepared the news.

01:16.177 --> 01:19.504
It is sufficient to spectacular welcome ceremony in Istanbul

01:19.529 --> 01:24.961
with flowers and songs to understand
how popular the Indian Guru Shri Mataji is.

01:28.617 --> 01:33.136
The 75-year-old Indian guru came on
a wheelchair to avoid getting tired.

01:33.168 --> 01:36.123
Devotees welcomed their Guru kneeling down before Her.

01:36.131 --> 01:37.948
Some had tears in their eyes.

01:43.178 --> 01:48.912
Not only Turks came to Sahaja Yoga conference in Istanbul.

01:48.962 --> 01:53.562
Gurunun müritleri otobüslerle
Rusya’dan Malezya’dan kalkıp geldiler.

01:57.417 --> 02:01.715
Shri Mataji continuous to receive
the high society in Her hotel room in Istanbul.

02:01.763 --> 02:06.470
A concrete example of the interest shown t
o Her are the shoes letf in front of the door.

02:08.895 --> 02:11.314
The devotees, knowing that Shri mataji likes flowers,

02:11.339 --> 02:14.319
they decorated the hotel room with flowers.

02:14.344 --> 02:18.354
There is a strong smell of  flowers
and incence in the room.

02:21.324 --> 02:26.458
One of the Shri Mataji’s visitors today is from
an old Turkish family of Eczacıbaşı.

02:26.483 --> 02:29.517
Nükhet Eczacıbaşı expressed her respect
by offering  flowers to Shri Mataji.

02:33.450 --> 02:37.549
Shri Mataji had a conversation with Nükhet Eczacıbaşı
who was sitting on her knees before Shri Mataji.

02:37.552 --> 02:40.863
Shri Mataji asked her if she fulfills her family duties.

02:40.928 --> 02:44.376
Shri Mataji:  but you were a daughter,
you looked after the parents,

02:44.384 --> 02:47.584
Nükhet Eczacıbaşı: I tried my best and

02:48.714 --> 02:50.500
Yoga helped me very much

02:50.564 --> 02:55.368
Just by looking into the young ladies face
Shri Mataji said that, she had a kidney problem.

02:55.393 --> 02:58.657
Indian Guru who is said that
She is able to cure AIDS and cancer

02:58.697 --> 03:03.924
took some sugar in Her hand
and put a healing power into the sugar.

03:04.046 --> 03:06.411
Shri Mataji:  But be carefull about your health now.

03:06.413 --> 03:07.086
Nükhet Eczacıbaşı: Yes,

03:07.111 --> 03:07.816
It is important.

03:07.841 --> 03:08.833
Nükhet Eczacıbaşı: Yes, yes, I will.

03:08.858 --> 03:10.970
Take this and this will cooldown you.

03:10.995 --> 03:12.995
Nükhet Eczacıbaşı: OK, I will.

03:13.021 --> 03:14.825
Shri Mataji:  And you will feel better.

03:14.850 --> 03:18.056
Nükhet Eczacıbaşı took the sugar and when she was leaving

03:18.064 --> 03:21.676
the room Shri Mataji again explained to her how to use sugar.

03:21.701 --> 03:27.030
Shri Mataji: Take it with a spoon and put more water.

03:27.049 --> 03:29.985
Like other guests who are impressed
in this way by the Indian Guru,

03:30.010 --> 03:33.055
we kneel down before Her hoping to learn Her secret.

03:33.079 --> 03:34.595
The first assesment is positive

03:34.620 --> 03:35.779
and Guru feels the energy.

03:35.804 --> 03:38.028
Shri Mataji: She has got it already

03:41.786 --> 03:44.930
Then together with Her assistant,
She makes a check up.

03:44.947 --> 03:47.250
Indian Guru does not find a physical ailment

03:47.258 --> 03:50.236
but She draws out attention to a mental problem.

03:50.446 --> 03:54.041
Yogi Mahajan : Do you have feelings in your hands?

03:54.338 --> 03:57.920
Shri Mataji: Now, you have to forgive, allright?

03:57.961 --> 04:00.325
Yogi Mahajan : You don’t forgive.

04:00.350 --> 04:04.246
You have to forgive. It is a mental problem.

04:05.804 --> 04:08.920
Shri Mataji: Now, better?

04:09.190 --> 04:11.412
Negative enegy is taken from the body

04:11.452 --> 04:14.198
and now the mind is brought
to state where it is ready to forgive.
